companyName: ETF Series Solutions Trust - Gadsden Dynamic Growth ETF
description:
The investment seeks total return.
 The fund is an actively-managed exchange-traded fund ("ETF") that seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing (i) approximately 80% of its total assets with exposure to global equity securities generally based on a long-term view of macroeconomic factors (the "strategic sleeve") and (ii) approximately 20% of its total assets to add or reduce exposure to one or more asset classes generally based on a short-term view of the market (the "tactical sleeve"). The fund may invest in futures contracts to gain long or short exposure to one or more asset classes.
